<doc>
  <member name="D3D12_ROOT_DESCRIPTOR">
    <summary>
      <para>Describes descriptors inline in the root signature version 1.0 that appear in shaders.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>
        <b>D3D12_ROOT_DESCRIPTOR</b> is the data type of the <b>Descriptor</b> member of <see cref="D3D12_ROOT_PARAMETER" />.
Use a <b>D3D12_ROOT_DESCRIPTOR</b> when you set <b>D3D12_ROOT_PARAMETER</b>'s <b>ParameterType</b> field to the D3D12_ROOT_PARAMETER_TYPE_CBV, D3D12_ROOT_PARAMETER_TYPE_SRV, or D3D12_ROOT_PARAMETER_TYPE_UAV members of <see cref="D3D12_ROOT_PARAMETER_TYPE" />.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/cd3dx12-root-descriptor">CD3DX12_ROOT_DESCRIPTOR</seealso>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/direct3d-12-structures">Core Structures</seealso>
    <seealso cref="D3D12_ROOT_DESCRIPTOR1" />
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/using-descriptors-directly-in-the-root-signature">Using descriptors directly in the root signature</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_ROOT_DESCRIPTOR.ShaderRegister">
    <summary>
      <para>The shader register.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
